FBIS4-31099 "dreeu108_h_94010" FBIS-EEU-94-108 Daily Report 4 Jun 1994 HUNGARY PESTI HIRLAP Suspends Publication PESTI HIRLAP Suspends Publication LD0406102094 Budapest Kossuth Radio Network in Hungarian 0700 GMT 4 Jun 94 LD0406102094 Budapest Kossuth Radio Network Hungarian BFN [Text] From Monday the publication PESTI HIRLAP [center-right daily] will be discontinued. The board of trustees of the 150 Years Foundation, the publisher, decided to suspend publication of the paper due to the publisher's difficult financial situation. The foundation's board of trustees, however, is ready to hold talks with its creditors on a debt settlement. It is also ready to hold talks with new investors on a possible restart or sale of PESTI HIRLAP.
